  "text": "According to the classification given by Rinaldi et al [CITATION_1] ], critical infrastructure interdependencies can be either physical, cyber, geographical, and/or logical. Among these four types of interdependencies, physical and geographical interdependencies seem to be more apparent and can be more easily identified (although an exhaustive list of interdependencies may never be reached).",
